A29. Find a publicly available AI-generated image, video, or audio clip, use at least one detection or verification tool to analyse it.

I use a website called Sightengine to detect an image I found on r/aiArt on Reddit. 
Sightengine not only tell something is ai or not, it also tell which AI generated the image.
In my case it predicted that the image is 98% to be generated by ai, and 94% to be generated by imagen.
